[[File:MarshallIslandsPSSlogo.png|right]] '''Republic of Marshall Islands Public School System''' ('''PSS''') is the public school system of the [[Marshall Islands]], headquartered in [[Majuro]].<ref>"[http://pss.edu.mh/en/about-us/location RMI Public School System Main Office]." Republic of Marshall Islands Public School System. Retrieved on February 21, 2018. "Ministry of Education, Sports, & Training Majuro, Majuro Atoll 96960, RMI"</ref> It was established in November 2013 by Public Law 2013-23.<ref>"[http://pss.edu.mh/en/about-us About Us]." Republic of Marshall Islands Public School System. Retrieved on February 21, 2018.</ref>
